## Gap Analysis

To reach $200,000/year, consulting must generate **$137,875/year** ($11,490/month) after the pension and CPP floor.

Key questions this raises:
- How many active Stealth EA clients/contracts are needed to sustain $137,875 in consulting revenue?
- What is the minimum consulting income at which you remain financially stable vs. comfortable vs. achieving targets?
- At what consulting revenue level does it make sense to re-evaluate the retirement decision?

