## OAS Consideration

OAS begins at age 65 (or deferred to 70 for a 36% boost):
- Standard 2024 OAS: ~$8,713/year at 65
- Clawback begins at **$90,997 net income** (2024) — full clawback at ~$148,179
- At your target income of $200,000, **OAS would be fully clawed back**
- At worst case ($62,125), OAS would be received in full — adds ~$8,713, bringing floor to **~$70,838**

